A formalisation of a tool similar to Smallfoot in HOL

The contents of this directory are

README ......................... This file
examples.txt ................... A file containing a short introduction
examples ....................... Directory containing examples
examples/non_solvable .......... Directory containing examples that are 
                                 designed to fail


